		#publications.background-alt
			h2.heading Publications
			.publications-block
				h3 Providing Occupancy as a Service with Databox
				h4 CitiFog 2018
				p In this paper we present Occupancy-as-a-Service (OaaS) implemented as an app on Databox.
				a(href='res/papers/citifog18-final7.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 An Information-Theoretic Approach to Time-Series Data Privacy
				h4 W-P2DS 2018 / EuroDW 2018
				p This paper presents a system for efficiently augmenting token-based access control with privacy-awareness without significantly impacting performance or utility.
				a(href='res/papers/a3-amar.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Building Accountability into the Internet of Things: The IoT Databox Model
				h4 Journal of Reliable Intelligent Environments December 2017
				p This paper outlines the IoT Databox model as a means of making the Internet of Things (IoT) accountable to individuals.
				a(href='res/papers/JREI-D-17-00019.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Balanced Message Distribution in Distributed Message Handling Systems
				h4 US Patent (serial number: 15/794440) 2017
				p This patent describes a combination of methodologies for arriving at near-optimal message distribution decisions in distributed messaging systems under specific constraints.
				a(href='javascript:alert("Coming soon!")') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Route-based Authorization and Discovery for Personal Data
				h4 EuroDW 2017
				p When faced with systems in which third party components need to advertise the availability of data they gather, while other such components need to access it, solutions for delegated authorisation and discovery APIs for interoperability are needed. This work explores possible solutions, and converges on a testable implementation.
				a(href='res/papers/eurodw17-final3.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Personal Data Management with the Databox: What's Inside the Box?
				h4 CAN 2016
				p A more detailed look at the Databox as it stood; a collection of physical and cloudhosted software components that provide for an individual data subject to manage, log and audit access to their data by other parties.
				a(href='res/papers/p49-mortier.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Privacy-Aware Infrastructure for Managing Personal Data
				h4 SIGCOMM 2016
				p A poster abstract giving an overview of Databox systems as they stood with a stronger focus on arbiter interactions.
				a(href='res/papers/p571-amar.pdf') PDF
			.publications-block
				h3 Incremental Dense Multi-modal 3D Scene Reconstruction
				h4 IROS 2015
				p In this paper, we propose a probabilistic model that efficiently exploits complementarity between different depth-sensing modalities for incremental dense scene reconstruction.
				a(href='res/papers/ondra2015iros.pdf') PDF

